{"word":"ἀποδικεῖν","slug":"ἀποδικεῖν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποδικεῖν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> of <el>ἀπέδικον</el>, aor2 with no <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> in use.\n<p/><i>to throw off</i> or <i>away</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}